import { Button, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow } from '@mui/material' import axios from 'axios' import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' const View= () => { var [users,SetUsers] = useState([]) useEffect(()=>{ axios.get("http://localhost:3005/view") .then((res)=>{ console.log(res.data) SetUsers(res.data) }) },[]) return (
Name Age Position Salary {users.map((val,i)=>{ return ( {val.ename} {val.eage} {val.eposition} {val.esalary} ) })}
) } export default View
